issues.description: SMIS is disabled.
issues.recommendation: SMIS will be enabled automatically.

issues.description: Profile Server_01 has one or more connections configured with Use-BIOS boot settings. OneView does not support profile connections configured with a mixture of Use-BIOS and other boot settings.
issues.recommendation: The Virtual Connect Use-BIOS boot setting will be automatically changed to not bootable in OneView.

issues.description: Profile Server_01 FCoE connection 3 does not have an associated network.  This connection will not be migrated because OneView does not allow server profile connections without an assigned network.
issues.recommendation: To migrate the server profile connection, assign a network or fabric to this connection. If virtual MAC or WWN addresses are configured, assigning a network or fabric to this connection will preserve these addresses.

issues.description: Profile Server_01 FCoE connection 1 is configured for factory MAC and a factory WWN of 10:00:40:A8:F0:2B:03:A1. The WWN for this connection may change after migration to OneView.
issues.recommendation: After the migration task has completed, validate the WWNs of the migrated profiles for any potential changes. If a WWN change occurred, change the SAN fabric and storage configuration to reflect the new WWNs before powering on the servers.
